---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Amplifly">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-32 pb-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Amplifly ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our service, including data obtained through the Oura Ring API. We comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable privacy laws.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">2.1 Oura Ring Data</h3>
        <p>When you connect your Oura Ring account, we collect and process the following data through Oura's API:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Sleep data (sleep stages, sleep score, sleep efficiency)</li>
          <li>Activity data (steps, calories, active time)</li>
          <li>Readiness scores and contributing factors</li>
          <li>Heart rate data (resting heart rate, heart rate variability)</li>
          <li>Other health metrics provided by Oura Ring API</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We only access the minimum amount of data necessary to provide our service.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your Oura Ring data exclusively to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Provide personalized recommendations for managing stress, sleep, and energy patterns</li>
          <li>Analyze patterns to improve our service</li>
          <li>Generate insights about your health and wellness</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We do not use your data for any other purposes without your explicit consent.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>All data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.2 or higher</li>
          <li>Data at rest is encrypted using industry-standard encryption</li>
          <li>We maintain strict access controls and authentication measures</li>
          <li>Regular security audits and updates are performed</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
        <p>We retain your Oura Ring data only as long as necessary to provide our service:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Data is automatically deleted when you disconnect your Oura Ring account</li>
          <li>You can request immediate deletion of your data at any time</li>
          <li>We comply with Oura's data retention policies</li>
          <li>Backup data is retained for up to 30 days before permanent deletion</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Service providers who assist in operating our service (under strict confidentiality agreements)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We do not share your data with third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR and other applicable laws, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Disconnect your Oura Ring account at any time</li>
          <li>Opt-out of data collection</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout> 